snippet.title: Game Boy Longplay [073] Parasol Stars
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: MadMatty

Classic Gameboy port of Parasol Stars. It s a complete run showing all worlds. The ending is abit ...minimal to say the least, I was expecting more.

I managed to collect matching Magic Items on one level allowing me to show the bonus level. In this bonus stage you can win 10 continues if you survive the time limit. Or could have taken the other door for 1 continue. Its a gamble with a big payoff.

To get good ending(as shown) 3 Matching Magic Stars are needed on Rainbow world in order to progress onto the remaining worlds. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
